ingredient: 1 boneless, skinless chicken breast (about ¾ lb.)*
4 whole pita breads (8 half round pockets)
2 oz. frozen spinach (1 cup when frozen)
1 cup long grain white rice, uncooked
1/3 cup sun dried tomato halves (about 7 pcs), sliced
4 oz. Monterrey Jack or Pepper Jack, shredded
1 4 oz. can diced mild green chiles
2 oz. queso fresco or Monterey jack
4 oz. can diced green chiles, drained
